snippet.textDisplay:
I'm literally at a loss for words,
I've started falling in love with Alec and his music these past few months and as much as I love all of his songs, this one is 100% my favourite, it's not only my favourite song by Alec, but my favourite song ever, it hits home and really touches the heart, you can tell by the way its written how personal this song is to Alec and I'm so glad he decided to share it.
Im sure this song resonates with a lot of people just like it does with me but the music video depicted it perfectly, the feeling this song is describing, like you're under water and can't breathe and there seems like no way out 💔 by far my favourite singer of all time 💕
